# Host-only artifacts that must NOT enter Docker build contexts. Without this,
# stale incremental-build cache files (e.g. tsbuildinfo) confuse the in-container
# `tsc -b` into thinking shared-schemas is already built, producing an image
# with no dist/ and ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND at runtime (see the AC-BOOT-00 e2e
# CI failure on 2026-04-19).

# Dependency trees — always re-resolved inside the container
**/node_modules

# Build outputs and incremental caches — never trust host state
**/dist
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Local secrets — must never land in an image
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
compose.override.yaml

# Test and coverage artifacts
coverage/
playwright-report/
test-results/
.playwright/

# Editor and VCS metadata
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.github
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store

# Claude Code harness files (not part of the running service)
.claude
CLAUDE.md

# Documentation — not needed at runtime
docs/
